column5: Feb 1st ice and walleye report ...well the ice is in great shape with alittle snow cover now ..Last night fishing was awesome lots of walleye being caught and a few Bows ..one guy got a 14.5 lb bow Nice Catch Fishlips.. there was guys that got big numbers of fish yesterday some with 2 fish some with 18 or more .. Fishfarmer how did you do last night ...
WOW...Great catch man thats a sweet lookin bow for sure !!!!.  .nice pics too,and that walleye is nice too....cheers
Hey Steve  How did the ice hold up today with all the heavy snow.  Will be out to see you in the morning  Cheers  Craig
I was wondering how long it would be before someone got an OOS chromer down there. Nice eye!
Ice is Fine ..and the fish are hungry..
Just 1 Steve and 3 other hits. My buddy got 1 also. See you tomorrow.
